267
00:16:14.230 --> 00:16:16.230
Aren't you?

268
00:16:16.230 --> 00:16:21.120
It's indeed Ella who framed.

269
00:16:21.120 --> 00:16:23.250
Ma'am, you've been fired?

270
00:16:23.250 --> 00:16:25.250
I'm asking, please leave the company.

271
00:16:25.250 --> 00:16:27.860
And who the hell are you?

272
00:16:27.860 --> 00:16:32.460
Oh, if you know, I got this job through my grandmother's connections.

273
00:16:32.460 --> 00:16:34.059
Go on now.

274
00:16:34.059 --> 00:16:35.059
Oh, come on.

275
00:16:35.059 --> 00:16:36.059
Let's go with me.

276
00:16:36.059 --> 00:16:37.379
Hey.

277
00:16:37.379 --> 00:16:38.379
Hey, hey, hey.

278
00:16:38.379 --> 00:16:40.889
Derry.

279
00:16:40.889 --> 00:16:41.980
I don't know.

280
00:16:41.980 --> 00:16:42.980
Nope, nope.

281
00:16:42.980 --> 00:16:44.139
No.

282
00:16:44.139 --> 00:16:47.139
I traced the IP address of the email sender.

283
00:16:47.139 --> 00:16:48.139
And guess what?

284
00:16:48.139 --> 00:16:50.399
Came from your home.

285
00:16:50.399 --> 00:16:56.580
You spread rumors and conspired to disgrace the company's reputation.

286
00:16:56.580 --> 00:16:58.580
