290
00:17:08.579 --> 00:17:09.579
Well said.

291
00:17:09.579 --> 00:17:14.309
Did he hear everything I just said?

292
00:17:14.309 --> 00:17:15.309
She's right.

293
00:17:15.309 --> 00:17:27.339
Thank you so much for helping me find the evidence.

294
00:17:27.339 --> 00:17:28.339
None of you to thank me.

295
00:17:28.339 --> 00:17:31.339
The boss asked me to help you specifically.

296
00:17:31.339 --> 00:17:32.339
He did?

297
00:17:32.339 --> 00:17:35.099
He's the best.

298
00:17:35.099 --> 00:17:38.190
I think I really like him.

299
00:17:38.190 --> 00:17:41.190
You know, not like romantically or anything.

300
00:17:41.190 --> 00:17:46.319
I can even act like a guy around him if you want and treat him like we're bros.

301
00:17:46.319 --> 00:17:47.319
Lucas.

302
00:17:47.319 --> 00:17:50.319
Should we discuss the divorce details with your wife?

303
00:17:50.319 --> 00:18:10.809
Right.

304
00:18:10.809 --> 00:18:13.809
I just want to say thank you for speaking up for me.

305
00:18:13.809 --> 00:18:16.809
And if you need anything, just let me know.

306
00:18:16.809 --> 00:18:18.349
Okay.

307
00:18:18.349 --> 00:18:19.990
Of course.

308
00:18:19.990 --> 00:18:21.990
You know what actually there's something you need to do?

309
00:18:21.990 --> 00:18:24.369
