310
00:18:24.369 --> 00:18:26.369
By some basic clothes.

311
00:18:26.369 --> 00:18:29.369
Thanks, but I already have plenty of clothes.

312
00:18:29.369 --> 00:18:30.369
Not for you.

313
00:18:30.369 --> 00:18:31.619
The company.

314
00:18:32.660 --> 00:18:36.660
We're going to go on a business trip next week and I need you to represent our image in the best way possible.

315
00:18:36.660 --> 00:18:40.700
Yeah, I'll get on it.

316
00:18:40.700 --> 00:18:44.740
Good.

317
00:18:44.740 --> 00:18:59.059
It's not bad to have a boss like him.

318
00:18:59.059 --> 00:19:00.059
I can't lose this job.

319
00:19:00.059 --> 00:19:01.059
Stop.

320
00:19:01.059 --> 00:19:10.799
Stop.

321
00:19:10.799 --> 00:19:14.180
