325
00:19:21.720 --> 00:19:23.720
By my lover, I haven't seen for me.

326
00:19:23.720 --> 00:19:24.720
Enough of your lies.

327
00:19:24.720 --> 00:19:25.720
I'm not lying.

328
00:19:25.720 --> 00:19:28.779
My name was Michelle.

329
00:19:28.779 --> 00:19:32.130
Then my husband left and he didn't come back.

330
00:19:32.130 --> 00:19:33.130
I changed my name.

331
00:19:33.130 --> 00:19:35.349
So he never find me.

332
00:19:35.349 --> 00:19:37.349
Is that why you're cheating on me?

333
00:19:37.349 --> 00:19:38.349
What?

334
00:19:38.349 --> 00:19:40.900
That bitch is cheating?

335
00:19:40.900 --> 00:19:41.900
I, uh...

336
00:19:41.900 --> 00:19:43.900
This is Lucas's divorce attorney.

337
00:19:43.900 --> 00:19:46.980
We need to discuss the alimony.

338
00:19:46.980 --> 00:19:48.019
Hello?

339
00:19:48.019 --> 00:19:50.240
Mrs. Herbert, are you there?

340
00:19:50.240 --> 00:19:54.799
Alright, well since you're here, let's talk divorce.

341
00:19:54.799 --> 00:19:57.089
Oh my God.

342
00:19:57.089 --> 00:19:58.089
His wife is...

